### 智能停车管理系统 API 测试脚本
### 基础地址: http://localhost:8080

### ============================================
### 1. 用户模块
### ============================================

### 1.1 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "openid": "test_openid_001",
  "nickname": "测试用户1",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar1.png"
}

### 1.2 获取用户信息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/info/1

### ============================================
### 2. 停车场模块
### ============================================

### 2.1 获取停车场列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/parking-lot/list

### 2.2 获取停车场详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/parking-lot/detail/1

### ============================================
### 3. 车位模块
### ============================================

### 3.1 获取所有车位列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/parking-space/list

### 3.2 获取可用车位
GET http://localhost:8080/api/parking-space/available

### ============================================
### 4. 预约模块
### ============================================

### 4.1 创建预约
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "parkingLotId": 1,
  "spaceId": 1,
  "startTime": "2026-05-28T10:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-05-28T12:00:00",
  "plateNumber": "京A12345"
}

### 4.2 获取用户预约列表
GET http://localhost:8080/reservation/list/1

### ============================================
### 5. 停车记录模块
### ============================================

### 5.1 车辆入场
POST http://localhost:8080/api/parking-record/entry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parkingLotId": 1,
  "spaceId": 1,
  "plateNumber": "京A12345",
  "entryTime": "2026-05-27T14:30:00"
}

### 5.2 车辆出场
POST http://localhost:8080/api/parking-record/exit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recordId": 1,
  "exitTime": "2026-05-27T16:45:00"
}

### 5.3 获取用户停车记录列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/parking-record/list/1

### 5.4 获取停车记录详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/parking-record/detail/1

### ============================================
### 6. 支付模块
### ============================================

### 6.1 创建支付订单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payment/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "recordId": 1,
  "amount": 24.00,
  "payMethod": "wechat"
}

### ============================================
### 7. 共享车位模块
### ============================================

### 7.1 创建共享记录
POST http://localhost:8080/share/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ownerId": 1,
  "spaceId": 1,
  "startTime": "2026-05-28T08:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-05-28T18:00:00",
  "pricePerHour": 5.00
}

### 7.2 获取用户共享记录
GET http://localhost:8080/share/list/1

### ============================================
### 8. 挪车模块
### ============================================

### 8.1 发起挪车请求
POST http://localhost:8080/move-car/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requesterId": 1,
  "spaceCode": "B2-015",
  "reason": "车辆挡住出口",
  "contactPhone": "13800138000"
}

### 8.2 获取挪车请求列表
GET http://localhost:8080/move-car/list/requester/1

### ============================================
### 9. 数据大屏模块
### ============================================

### 9.1 获取仪表盘数据
GET http://localhost:8080/dashboard/data

### 9.2 获取热力图数据
GET http://localhost:8080/heatmap/lot/1

### ============================================
### 10. 健康检查模块
### ============================================

### 10.1 创建健康检查记录
POST http://localhost:8080/health-check/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recordId": 1,
  "checkItems": [
    {"item": "轮胎", "status": 0},
    {"item": "车窗", "status": 0}
  ]
}

### 10.2 获取停车记录的健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/health-check/list/record/1
